{"tid":1629171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞：法官下令月底前全面聆訊《禁蒙面法》　郭榮鏗：顯示法庭認為法例衍生憲制問題","createTime":"2019-10-06T07:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T07:05:51.000Z","uid":223407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a27feef899c84b6255f7a08ca37a4b971740bab","tid":1629171,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"24名民主派立法會議員要求就《禁止蒙面規例》頒布臨時禁制令，但法庭拒絕。民主派立法會議員郭榮鏗庭後見記者時表示，法庭今日罕見下令雙方盡快確定日期在月底前舉行全面聆訊，顯示法庭接受申請人一方說法，禁蒙面法衍生的憲制問題惹來重大公眾關注，及牽涉行政長可否繞過立法會立法等重要問題，郭榮鏗指，相信法官林雲浩亦看見引用緊急法訂立禁蒙面法極有可能違憲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/法官下令月底前全面聆訊-禁蒙面法-郭榮鏗-顯示法庭認為法例衍生憲制問題/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%86%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=b93021fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%86%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&h=189ce20f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/法官下令月底前全面聆訊-禁蒙面法-郭榮鏗-顯示法庭認為法例衍生憲制問題/</a>"}]}